name: Loving you to the Moon
description:
I hand textured the outside edge of a sterling silver 3/4" round disc and handstamped "Loving you to the moon and back" with my custom script font. The 1/2" disc holds the name of your loved one.
Accented with a freshwater pearl and they hang on sterling 18" bead chain.


**Custom Orders***
I would love to make a special piece just for you. Contact me and I will work with you on your custom piece of Word Art.

*Note from artist*
I hand-stamp each piece one letter at a time. Expect some variations in the spacing of the letters. It's what makes it unique and one of a kind.

***Shipping***
Item will arrive in a ribbon tied gift box, ready for gift giving. All of my handstamped items come with a free polishing cloth.

name: Double Love handstamped name tags
description:

Hand stamped with my custom hand script font.
Two sterling silver tags measure 5/8" each.
I can fit up to 5 characters across and 10 -12 characters curved on the bottom.
This listing is for two tags with a birthstone on each and your choice of chain in either box or bead and 16" or 18".

At checkout please list your names and birth months along with your choice of chain, in the "message to seller" box.
